messages.message: added a new zoom meeting to the UATs working session!
Will be a couple min late

btw i forgot to invite you ahead of time @Sherif :sweat_smile: so no worries if you can't join this time!

for future context, we create a release branch from master every 2 weeks -> we then do user-acceptance testing (UAT) on that release branch before deploying it to prod (aihub.instabase.com (http://aihub.instabase.com))

some of these UATs are automated (Cypress tests, system tests, golden tests), and some are manual and checked off in Testmo

we do some UATs together to share knowledge and hold each other accountable, as suggested by Prateek (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C08L4K42H9C/p1745511402576449)!
asked about running Cypress tests on aihub-uat  https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CGQ7BD72A/p1747336406400729?thread_ts=1747079244.596959&cid=CGQ7BD72A
